                            <comment id="17839055" author="JIRAUSER285918" created="Fri, 19 Apr 2024 16:58:53 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks for reporting the issue, I confirm the bug, it is because, in the case of the CXF endpoint, the logging size limit is set to 0 by default which is not expected/wanted. As a workaround, you can simply set the &lt;a href=&quot;https://camel.apache.org/components/4.4.x/cxf-component.html#_endpoint_query_option_loggingSizeLimit&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;query parameter &lt;tt&gt;loggingSizeLimit&lt;/tt&gt;&lt;/a&gt; to a specific value knowing that &lt;tt&gt;-1&lt;/tt&gt; means no limit&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="17840714" author="JIRAUSER285918" created="Thu, 25 Apr 2024 09:04:31 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Corresponding PRs:&lt;/p&gt;

